{
  "stem": "1858.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 297.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I didn't want to let go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But my father took my hand and said, come on, we have to go.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And my father, holding my hand, led me to the Umschlagplatz, to the point where I had to report.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "On the way, he tried to instill hope in me and kept on saying, this is coming to an end soon.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Remember, we shall be waiting for you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Remember, you have to come back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "So be strong and live and come back because we wait for you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I didn't realize then that my father knew that the end is so near.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And he fabricated this tale to perhaps give me a little more time to perhaps help me survive.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I believed what my father told me was true.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Had I known what happened only two weeks after I have left, I would never have made it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I try to think of my father-- having children-- what they did to this man.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He, who was ready to give his life for his little girl, for me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He, having to take me by my hand, delivering to the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He, who was ready to die to save me, finding himself so totally, totally-- rendering him so totally useless, so powerless, how terrible he must have felt.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What have they done to our people, even before they killed us?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to the Durchgangslager-- like that was a temporary camp from which I was to be shipped eventually.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And while there, they asked us to give up any valuables.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like, I had a tiny little suitcase with me, in which I had my little album with photographs of my girlfriends.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had a little book in which all my girlfriends wrote something for me, you know, from before the war.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
